for professional women.

507
00:23:05,440 --> 00:23:06,440
Come on. Let's look over here.

508
00:23:08,790 --> 00:23:10,260
This piece is particularly suitable.

509
00:23:10,260 --> 00:23:11,110
Look,

510
00:23:11,110 --> 00:23:13,860
from the fabric to the cut,
everything looks very high-end.

511
00:23:14,060 --> 00:23:15,060
Why don't you try it on?

512
00:23:15,060 --> 00:23:16,580
I won't buy it. Just get it for my mom.

513
00:23:16,580 --> 00:23:18,340
Mom, just pick one. I don't need it.

514
00:23:19,300 --> 00:23:20,400
Actually, this piece of clothing,

515
00:23:20,400 --> 00:23:21,380
both of you can wear it.

516
00:23:21,380 --> 00:23:23,260
Wearing it, you look like sisters.

517
00:23:23,260 --> 00:23:25,340
Your mom looks younger wearing it.

518
00:23:25,340 --> 00:23:27,580
And you, Miss, look elegant
and graceful wearing it.

519
00:23:28,200 --> 00:23:30,340
We really haven't worn
the same clothes before.

520
00:23:30,860 --> 00:23:32,260
There's no need for that.

521
00:23:32,540 --> 00:23:34,580
Try it on.
Get us one each and we'll try it on.

522
00:23:34,580 --> 00:23:36,380
Alright, let me get your sizes
for you two.

523
00:23:36,860 --> 00:23:38,100
Come on. Please follow this way.

524
00:23:38,300 --> 00:23:39,220
Let's go.

525
00:23:43,020 --> 00:23:44,620
(Retail Price 2,600 Yuan)

526
00:23:47,420 --> 00:23:49,500
