527
00:23:50,020 --> 00:23:52,060
In the past, following your dad around

528
00:23:52,060 --> 00:23:53,820
was a complete mess.

529
00:23:54,060 --> 00:23:55,300
I can't even remember to do

530
00:23:55,300 --> 00:23:58,340
something memorable with family.

531
00:23:59,170 --> 00:24:00,030
Alright.

532
00:24:00,040 --> 00:24:02,780
In the blink of an eye,
you've grown so much.

533
00:24:04,260 --> 00:24:06,020
Mom, I have grown up.

534
00:24:06,020 --> 00:24:07,220
Why do we wear a parent-child outfit?

535
00:24:07,220 --> 00:24:08,240
Maybe we should just forget it.

536
00:24:08,780 --> 00:24:10,580
I'm just afraid that if I blink again,

537
00:24:11,540 --> 00:24:12,860
there won't be a chance.

538
00:24:13,820 --> 00:24:15,380
What nonsense are you talking about?

539
00:24:17,300 --> 00:24:18,820
I am not talking nonsense.

540
00:24:19,580 --> 00:24:20,860
I've come to understand.

541
00:24:21,260 --> 00:24:24,580
We must cherish the present
and live in the moment.

542
00:24:29,710 --> 00:24:31,340
- It's really nice.
