too flashy for my age?

552
00:24:45,530 --> 00:24:46,420
You two sisters,

553
00:24:46,420 --> 00:24:48,660
no, when you and
your daughter stand together,

554
00:24:48,660 --> 00:24:50,140
if the designer sees,

555
