- Please come this way, you two.

562
00:25:04,610 --> 00:25:05,500
Take a couple of shots.

563
00:25:05,510 --> 00:25:07,140
Sister, look this way.

564
00:25:08,420 --> 00:25:10,140
Beautiful.

565
00:25:10,860 --> 00:25:12,660
Sister, you look like a professional.

566
00:25:12,660 --> 00:25:13,900
You are so photogenic.

567
00:25:14,380 --> 00:25:16,340
Look at this pose and this expression.

568
00:25:16,380 --> 00:25:17,420
So relaxed.

569
00:25:18,140 --> 00:25:19,140
Really looks good.

570
00:25:19,180 --> 00:25:20,100
By the way, Sister,

571
00:25:20,140 --> 00:25:22,380
let's take these two pieces of
clothing back together.

572
00:25:22,380 --> 00:25:23,460
When we check out later,

573
00:25:23,620 --> 00:25:25,140
I'll personally give you a 5% discount,

574
00:25:25,140 --> 00:25:26,940
