575
00:25:29,140 --> 00:25:29,980
Okay.

576
00:25:30,380 --> 00:25:31,620
Alright, come on.

577
00:25:31,620 --> 00:25:32,900
Let's take a few more photos.

578
00:25:33,660 --> 00:25:35,180
Okay, let's change the pose.

579
00:25:35,940 --> 00:25:36,940
Get a bit closer.

580
00:25:37,100 --> 00:25:38,940
Good, really nice.

581
00:25:40,860 --> 00:25:41,940
Sorry, Lady.

582
00:25:41,940 --> 00:25:43,460
