583
00:25:43,860 --> 00:25:45,100
What is Ant Credit Pay?

584
00:25:45,940 --> 00:25:46,860
It's nothing.

585
00:25:47,420 --> 00:25:48,940
I clicked the wrong thing, sorry.

586
00:25:51,660 --> 00:25:52,500
Okay.

587
00:25:54,180 --> 00:25:55,100
Alright.

588
00:26:01,860 --> 00:26:02,700
Here you go.

589
00:26:03,040 --> 00:26:03,900
Thank you.

590
00:26:03,900 --> 00:26:05,140
My daughter is really something.

591
00:26:05,140 --> 00:26:06,950
I said I would do it,
but she insisted not to.

592
00:26:07,700 --> 00:26:09,140
Your daughter is so filial.

593
00:26:09,140 --> 00:26:10,660
Your blessings are yet to come.

594
00:26:10,660 --> 00:26:12,860
Sister, let's add each other
on WeChat later.

595
00:26:12,860 --> 00:26:14,860
I'll send all those photos to you.

596
00:26:14,860 --> 00:26:16,940
Whenever our store
has new arrivals or events,

597
00:26:16,940 --> 00:26:18,310
I'll notify you immediately.

598
00:26:18,310 --> 00:26:19,660
- Add my daughter instead.
- Okay.

599
00:26:19,660 --> 00:26:20,900
I don't often stay in Shanghai.

600
00:26:20,940 --> 00:26:21,780
Okay.

601
00:26:22,060 --> 00:26:23,420
Lady, shall we add
each other on WeChat?

602
00:26:28,420 --> 00:26:29,660
It's like this, Chen.

603
00:26:30,340 --> 00:26:32,540
I'm a bit tight on money lately,

604
00:26:32,540 --> 00:26:34,140
so I'd like to ask
if I can have a few days off

605
00:26:34,140 --> 00:26:35,660
for this month's rent.

606
00:26:35,700 --> 00:26:38,140
Just one week, and I'll
immediately transfer the money to you.

607
00:26:40,860 --> 00:26:42,140
Alright, thank you, Chen.

608
00:26:43,140 --> 00:26:44,140
Alright, bye.

609
00:26:57,720 --> 00:26:58,650
It's not easy for my mom

610
00:26:59,660 --> 00:27:01,420
to come to Shanghai.

611
00:27:01,660 --> 00:27:03,660
I definitely want her to
have a great time.

612
00:27:06,860 --> 00:27:08,940
The meal and those
two pieces of clothing yesterday,

613
00:27:08,940 --> 00:27:10,380
if my mom had to pay for them,

614
00:27:10,380 --> 00:27:12,100
I would feel guilty for a lifetime.

615
00:27:12,180 --> 00:27:15,660
But it was really expensive.

616
00:27:18,900 --> 00:27:22,660
I used to be able to pay the rent.

617
00:27:22,860 --> 00:27:24,620
But now I don't have a job.

618
00:27:24,620 --> 00:27:25,470
I resigned.

619
00:27:25,480 --> 00:27:27,660
I can't tell my mom
about the resignation.

620
00:27:28,140 --> 00:27:29,660
Actually, I could tell her, but

621
00:27:30,100 --> 00:27:32,100
I just don't know how to approach it.

622
00:27:33,140 --> 00:27:33,980
So I...

623
00:27:35,940 --> 00:27:36,860
What do you think?

624
00:27:50,340 --> 00:27:51,620
How did you fall asleep?

625
00:27:53,000 --> 00:27:54,860
Weren't you just opening
the door for me?

626
00:27:54,860 --> 00:27:56,140
Weren't you awake?

627
00:27:58,620 --> 00:28:00,380
- Get up.
- I slept too late last night.

628
00:28:00,560 --> 00:28:01,460
Just sleep a little longer.

629
00:28:07,940 --> 00:28:09,940
You're not even awake yet,
but your actions are so skillful.

630
00:28:09,940 --> 00:28:11,340
Do you hug anyone who comes by?

631
00:28:11,340 --> 00:28:12,420
How could that be possible?

632
00:28:13,940 --> 00:28:15,340
Did you hear what I said?

633
00:28:15,620 --> 00:28:16,620
I heard it.

634
00:28:17,660 --> 00:28:18,940
Then repeat it to me.

635
00:28:26,380 --> 00:28:28,940
You said your mom has had a hard life.

636
00:28:29,060 --> 00:28:30,480
It's not easy for her to
come to Shanghai.

637
00:28:30,480 --> 00:28:31,940
You want to take her
to experience it well.

638
00:28:32,140 --> 00:28:34,180
But the consumption in Shanghai
is really too high.

639
00:28:34,940 --> 00:28:35,940
And also,

640
00:28:36,420 --> 00:28:37,940
you don't know how to tell your mom

641
00:28:37,940 --> 00:28:39,100
about your resignation.

642
00:28:41,420 --> 00:28:42,940
You really heard everything.

643
00:28:43,460 --> 00:28:44,900
Weren't you asleep?

644
00:28:45,460 --> 00:28:47,940
When I'm asleep, my mind is awake.

645
00:28:48,180 --> 00:28:49,420
You're really amazing.

646
00:28:53,940 --> 00:28:55,140
Don't be angry, okay?

647
00:28:56,220 --> 00:28:57,300
I'll take you to make money.

648
00:29:00,490 --> 00:29:01,660
Aren't you short of money?

649
00:29:02,200 --> 00:29:03,040
How to earn it?

650
00:29:13,060 --> 00:29:14,770
Ever since I started
doing stand-up comedy,

651
00:29:14,770 --> 00:29:16,140
I almost stopped dating.

652
00:29:16,140 --> 00:29:16,980
Because I found out,

653
00:29:16,980 --> 00:29:19,460
preparing for a date is much harder
than preparing for a show.

654
00:29:19,460 --> 00:29:20,660
Every time I go on a date,

655
00:29:20,660 --> 00:29:23,140
I can't find the right clothes
and makeup.

656
00:29:23,140 --> 00:29:24,340
It can't be too sexy,

657
00:29:24,340 --> 00:29:25,900
or the man will feel insecure.

658
00:29:26,900 --> 00:29:28,110
It can't be too plain,

659
00:29:28,110 --> 00:29:30,520
(Income +200 yuan)
or men will feel you're an obedient woman.

660
00:29:33,660 --> 00:29:34,590
As for me, I especially hope

661
00:29:34,590 --> 00:29:35,880
WeChat introduces a membership feature.

662
00:29:35,880 --> 00:29:37,310
If it comes out,
I will definitely buy it.

663
00:29:37,620 --> 00:29:39,160
It is to force restore

664
00:29:39,160 --> 00:29:40,940
the message that the other party
has already recalled.

665
00:29:40,940 --> 00:29:43,140
You sent this message to my phone.

666
00:29:43,180 --> 00:29:44,940
- Does it belong to me now?
- Yes.

667
00:29:45,060 --> 00:29:46,420
How dare you take back
what belongs to me

668
00:29:46,420 --> 00:29:48,180
(Income +200 yuan)
from my phone?

669
00:29:50,240 --> 00:29:54,860
♪Ignored a few missed calls♪

670
00:29:54,860 --> 00:29:58,720
♪Just walked away alone♪

671
00:29:58,870 --> 00:30:03,560
♪Is this how it's like♪

672
00:30:03,560 --> 00:30:08,040
♪Couldn't find an answer♪

673
00:30:08,040 --> 00:30:10,920
♪Is this how it's like♪

674
00:30:10,940 --> 00:30:12,340
Collecting money.

675
00:30:13,700 --> 00:30:15,140
What the hell are you guys doing?

676
00:30:15,620 --> 00:30:17,100
Didn't we agree on a pair show?

677
00:30:17,660 --> 00:30:19,420
Yes, we are performing stand-up comedy.

678
00:30:19,940 --> 00:30:21,900
Didn't we discuss this
with the labor agency?

679
00:30:21,900 --> 00:30:23,420
Alright, I don't want to hear anymore.

680
00:30:27,140 --> 00:30:27,980
Here.

681
00:30:29,940 --> 00:30:31,140
Didn't we agree on 300?

682
00:30:31,140 --> 00:30:32,460
Why are you only giving 200?

683
00:30:32,700 --> 00:30:33,900
No, you owe us 100 yuan.

684
00:30:33,940 --> 00:30:35,420
You're lucky to get any money at all.

685
00:30:35,420 --> 00:30:37,410
Do you know this is called
goods not as described?

686
00:30:37,420 --> 00:30:39,180
More seriously,
it's called false marketing.

687
00:30:39,180 --> 00:30:40,800
Do you know the nature of this matter?

688
00:30:40,800 --> 00:30:42,100
(Unstoppable Benefits Ignite Room)
Why?

689
00:30:42,100 --> 00:30:43,340
Didn't I already mention it?

690
00:30:44,140 --> 00:30:45,420
Do you still feel wronged?

691
00:30:45,420 --> 00:30:47,620
I clearly stated my requirements
with the labor agency.

692
00:30:47,620 --> 00:30:48,940
Pair Show.

693
00:30:48,940 --> 00:30:50,600
What you two are doing
is either crosstalk

694
00:30:50,600 --> 00:30:51,440
or sketch comedy.

695
00:30:51,620 --> 00:30:52,940
Isn't that goods not as described?

696
00:30:53,940 --> 00:30:55,460
Do you want that 100 yuan?

697
00:30:55,460 --> 00:30:56,660
Go find the labor agency.

698
00:30:56,660 --> 00:30:58,100
We also explained it clearly to...

699
00:30:58,100 --> 00:30:59,140
Forget it.

700
00:31:00,140 --> 00:31:02,140
It doesn't sound like
it's entirely his fault.

701
00:31:02,400 --> 00:31:03,860
We've been arguing with him
for a long time,

702
00:31:03,860 --> 00:31:04,900
not to mention wasting time

703
00:31:04,900 --> 00:31:06,440
and hurting both
the mind and the body.

704
00:31:07,040 --> 00:31:07,900
Otherwise,

705
00:31:07,940 --> 00:31:09,940
the next time I buy health products
for my mom,

706
00:31:09,940 --> 00:31:11,140
I'll get you some as well.

707
00:31:11,380 --> 00:31:13,140
You really overestimate
our capabilities.

708
00:31:13,140 --> 00:31:15,140
Now let alone buying health products
for your mom,

709
00:31:15,140 --> 00:31:17,140
it's difficult just to
maintain our own health.

710
00:31:17,660 --> 00:31:18,900
You reminded me.

711
00:31:18,940 --> 00:31:19,940
I need to calculate.

712
00:31:21,660 --> 00:31:27,340
Today we spent 40 yuan on food,

713
00:31:27,620 --> 00:31:30,620
12 yuan on the subway,
with an income of 200 yuan.

714
00:31:30,900 --> 00:31:33,660
Net profit of 148 yuan.

715
00:31:34,460 --> 00:31:35,420
That's great.

716
00:31:36,340 --> 00:31:37,900
We haven't even counted dinner yet.

717
00:31:44,380 --> 00:31:45,900
I bought this at the supermarket.

718
00:31:45,940 --> 00:31:47,420
Discount price, five yuan.

719
00:31:47,660 --> 00:31:49,620
Tonight I'll have a
western food dinner.

720
00:31:50,940 --> 00:31:52,380
Sliced toast and western food?

721
00:31:52,380 --> 00:31:54,660
Exactly, steamed bun is Chinese food.

722
00:31:54,860 --> 00:31:57,340
Let's see how you
turn it into western food.

723
00:32:29,420 --> 00:32:30,260
I'm coming.

724
00:32:31,380 --> 00:32:32,220
Who are you?

725
00:32:38,900 --> 00:32:40,420
Hello, I'm looking for Xiuya.

726
00:32:40,700 --> 00:32:41,620
Who are you?

727
00:32:41,620 --> 00:32:42,660
I'm the landlady here.

728
00:32:43,660 --> 00:32:44,630
I'm Xiuya's mom.

729
00:32:44,630 --> 00:32:45,710
Xiuya is not here right now.

730
00:32:45,710 --> 00:32:46,940
Come in. Have a seat.

731
00:32:46,940 --> 00:32:47,780
Okay.

732
00:32:49,940 --> 00:32:51,340
Here, have some water.

733
00:32:51,660 --> 00:32:52,500
Thank you.

734
00:32:53,620 --> 00:32:55,180
A couple of days ago, she called me

735
00:32:55,240 --> 00:32:57,140
and mentioned that
she seemed to be in trouble.

736
00:32:57,140 --> 00:32:59,140
Be in trouble? Really?

737
00:32:59,140 --> 00:33:00,910
She didn't explain clearly,
and I didn't ask.

738
00:33:01,420 --> 00:33:02,360
But still,

739
00:33:02,360 --> 00:33:04,140
she's young, and I'm worried
there's something wrong.

740
00:33:04,140 --> 00:33:05,420
So I came over to check on her.

741
00:33:06,860 --> 00:33:07,940
What could have happened?

742
00:33:10,340 --> 00:33:13,140
Actually, she's been renting
my place for two years.

743
00:33:13,460 --> 00:33:15,340
She's always lived there
without any issues.

744
00:33:15,620 --> 00:33:17,460
The rent has always been paid on time.

745
00:33:17,940 --> 00:33:18,940
But I think

746
00:33:19,340 --> 00:33:21,140
she might have encountered
some difficulties.

747
00:33:22,860 --> 00:33:24,900
Did she not pay the rent this month?

748
00:33:25,940 --> 00:33:27,620
This child is really considerate.

749
00:33:27,940 --> 00:33:30,660
She holds back unpleasant
information, and it's nothing major.

750
00:33:30,700 --> 00:33:31,940
I also said at the time

751
00:33:31,940 --> 00:33:33,660
that a few days' grace is not a problem.

752
00:33:35,660 --> 00:33:37,340
How much is it? I'll give it to you now.

753
00:33:37,620 --> 00:33:39,140
No, it's not what I meant.

754
00:33:40,140 --> 00:33:40,980
4,500 yuan.

755
00:33:41,940 --> 00:33:43,180
Alright, I'll get it for you.

756
00:33:43,180 --> 00:33:44,020
Okay.

757
00:33:50,420 --> 00:33:52,140
Here, I don't have an envelope either.

758
00:33:52,420 --> 00:33:53,380
Count it.

759
00:33:53,660 --> 00:33:54,500
Okay.

760
00:33:54,700 --> 00:33:56,330
You still carry cash when you go out?

761
00:33:56,330 --> 00:33:57,710
Nowadays,
we usually use mobile transfer.

762
00:33:57,710 --> 00:33:58,660
It's really convenient.

763
00:33:59,140 --> 00:34:00,140
Getting older,

764
00:34:00,140 --> 00:34:01,450
I'm not good at using
the mobile phone.

765
00:34:01,940 --> 00:34:02,900
How could that be?

766
00:34:04,660 --> 00:34:05,500
Alright.

767
00:34:06,870 --> 00:34:09,300
A few days ago, she said the washing
machine didn't work well.

768
00:34:09,300 --> 00:34:11,140
I'll find someone to fix it.

769
00:34:11,140 --> 00:34:12,490
Alright, thank you for the trouble.

770
00:34:12,490 --> 00:34:13,340
Okay, goodbye.

771
00:34:13,460 --> 00:34:14,300
Alright.

772
00:34:16,500 --> 00:34:17,460
Thank you.

773
00:34:17,500 --> 00:34:18,340
Goodbye.

774
00:35:02,940 --> 00:35:03,780
Wait a moment.

775
00:35:05,500 --> 00:35:06,340
My mom.

776
00:35:08,980 --> 00:35:09,820
Hello, Mom.

777
00:35:10,140 --> 00:35:11,900
Ya, why haven't you come back yet?

778
00:35:11,900 --> 00:35:12,790
Still working overtime?

779
00:35:13,620 --> 00:35:14,460
Yes.

780
00:35:14,460 --> 00:35:16,140
I still have a special report to write.

781
00:35:18,340 --> 00:35:19,460
How much longer will it take?

782
00:35:20,420 --> 00:35:21,300
It should be soon.

783
00:35:21,300 --> 00:35:22,460
I'll be back right away.

784
00:35:23,100 --> 00:35:26,180
Alright, the food is kept warm
for you in the pot.

785
00:35:26,420 --> 00:35:27,260
Okay.

786
00:35:27,980 --> 00:35:28,820
Bye.

787
00:35:29,980 --> 00:35:31,100
You're good.

788
00:35:32,180 --> 00:35:33,660
Lies come out so easily.

789
00:35:35,460 --> 00:35:37,140
Is there any other way?

790
00:35:39,660 --> 00:35:42,100
Go back and don't keep your mom waiting.

791
00:35:44,140 --> 00:35:45,300
Stay another five minutes.

792
00:35:47,400 --> 00:35:49,410
Wait until you walk with me
past that intersection.

793
00:35:54,260 --> 00:35:55,220
Why are you laughing?

794
00:35:55,460 --> 00:35:58,020
I feel like we were just
having a normal relationship.

795
00:35:58,460 --> 00:35:59,340
Now then,

796
00:36:00,060 --> 00:36:02,500
it's like having an affair.

797
00:36:03,980 --> 00:36:06,180
From now on, you'll be
my shadow boyfriend.

798
00:36:06,180 --> 00:36:07,400
Am I someone who can't be seen?

799
00:36:07,980 --> 00:36:08,940
No,

800
00:36:09,300 --> 00:36:10,740
the meaning of "shadow" is

801
00:36:14,900 --> 00:36:17,260
like a shadow, always together,
never apart.

802
00:37:18,980 --> 00:37:20,100
Mom, I'm back.

803
00:37:20,180 --> 00:37:21,020
You're back.

804
00:37:21,160 --> 00:37:22,340
Come on. Wash your hands for dinner.

805
00:37:22,340 --> 00:37:23,180
Okay.

806
00:37:37,980 --> 00:37:38,980
It smells so good.

807
00:37:40,060 --> 00:37:41,900
It's so nice to come home

808
00:37:41,900 --> 00:37:43,580
to Mom's cooking.

809
00:37:43,980 --> 00:37:45,980
Alright, stop with the glowing terms.

810
00:37:46,460 --> 00:37:47,300
Come on.

811
00:37:48,420 --> 00:37:49,620
Let me get you some soup first.

812
00:37:49,620 --> 00:37:50,460
Okay.

813
00:37:50,700 --> 00:37:51,700
Have some warm soup.

814
00:37:57,300 --> 00:37:59,220
The landlady came today.

815
00:38:00,060 --> 00:38:02,020
I paid the rent first.

816
00:38:03,020 --> 00:38:04,420
I told her

817
00:38:04,420 --> 00:38:05,940
I'd give it to her next week.

818
00:38:06,390 --> 00:38:08,320
The company's accountant
went on a business trip.

819
00:38:08,320 --> 00:38:09,620
The salary hasn't been paid yet.

820
00:38:11,020 --> 00:38:12,220
She was not at ease.

821
00:38:12,220 --> 00:38:14,460
When it comes to money,
we can't be careless.

822
00:38:16,340 --> 00:38:18,260
Once I get my salary, I'll pay you back.

823
00:38:18,460 --> 00:38:21,460
Alright, between close family members,
don't talk about repayment.

824
00:38:22,160 --> 00:38:23,480
But it still needs to be returned.

825
00:38:24,900 --> 00:38:27,740
By the way, when I was tidying up,
in your room,

826
00:38:29,300 --> 00:38:30,460
there was a little red book.

827
00:38:30,700 --> 00:38:32,700
What was written all over it?

828
00:38:33,940 --> 00:38:34,780
That one?

829
00:38:36,940 --> 00:38:40,700
It is just some interesting things
I come across,

830
00:38:40,700 --> 00:38:43,220
I just note them down.

831
00:38:43,220 --> 00:38:44,500
I find it quite fun.

832
00:38:45,060 --> 00:38:46,500
You have this hobby?

833
00:38:47,700 --> 00:38:48,540
Yeah.

834
00:38:51,260 --> 00:38:52,100
What's wrong?

835
00:38:53,420 --> 00:38:55,460
Take a look. Come on. Wipe it off.

836
00:38:55,460 --> 00:38:56,460
I'll go wash.

837
00:39:04,300 --> 00:39:09,100
(Advertising Department, Shi: Why
do I miss you as soon as we part?)

838
00:39:28,420 --> 00:39:29,260
Xiuya,

839
00:39:29,620 --> 00:39:30,460
are you going out?

840
00:39:31,300 --> 00:39:32,460
Yes, workplace.

841
00:39:32,980 --> 00:39:34,580
Do you have to work this weekend?

842
00:39:36,260 --> 00:39:37,900
Well, I happen to be free too.

843
00:39:37,900 --> 00:39:39,500
How about I go with you?

844
00:39:39,500 --> 00:39:41,310
It's also a good chance
to get some fresh air.

845
00:39:41,940 --> 00:39:42,780
No.

846
00:39:44,020 --> 00:39:45,940
It's my colleague's engagement ceremony.

847
00:39:45,940 --> 00:39:47,460
It's not very convenient for you to go.

848
00:39:49,100 --> 00:39:50,460
Alright, that's fine.

849
00:39:51,200 --> 00:39:52,370
Will you come back for dinner?

850
00:39:54,020 --> 00:39:55,100
Today I...

851
00:39:56,460 --> 00:39:59,300
I will be back quite late today.

852
00:39:59,300 --> 00:40:00,940
Mom, don't wait for me.

853
00:40:00,940 --> 00:40:02,260
Get some rest early, bye.

854
00:40:39,540 --> 00:40:42,380
(Zheng Hao)

855
00:40:52,020 --> 00:40:53,620
Hello, are you Zheng Hao?

856
00:40:54,020 --> 00:40:55,460
I am Xiuya's mom.

857
00:40:56,460 --> 00:40:57,500
Hello, Auntie.

858
00:40:58,020 --> 00:40:59,060
Hello.

859
00:41:00,260 --> 00:41:02,300
Did Xiuya tell you I came to Shanghai?

860
00:41:02,980 --> 00:41:04,460
She said you

861
00:41:04,710 --> 00:41:07,020
were on a business trip
and didn't know when you'd be back.

862
00:41:09,980 --> 00:41:10,820
Yes,

863
00:41:11,460 --> 00:41:13,100
I will try to return
as soon as possible.

864
00:41:13,100 --> 00:41:14,620
Auntie, do you need something?

865
00:41:15,420 --> 00:41:16,740
Well, I'm not rushing you.

866
00:41:16,980 --> 00:41:18,340
I just miss you.

867
00:41:18,460 --> 00:41:20,620
I wish you could come back
so I could see you.

868
00:41:27,180 --> 00:41:28,020
Hello?

869
00:41:28,340 --> 00:41:29,180
Zheng Hao.

870
00:41:31,500 --> 00:41:32,940
Hello? Are you still there?

871
00:41:33,420 --> 00:41:34,260
I'm here.

872
00:41:34,260 --> 00:41:36,260
I just received a job message.

873
00:41:37,400 --> 00:41:38,700
Auntie, I'll do it as soon as possible.

874
00:41:38,880 --> 00:41:39,790
I have another meeting here.

875
00:41:39,790 --> 00:41:40,960
I'll get back to my job first.

876
00:41:40,980 --> 00:41:41,820
Goodbye, Auntie.

877
00:41:42,980 --> 00:41:44,020
Alright.

878
00:41:44,060 --> 00:41:46,020
Your job is important. Let's hang up.

879
