♪Stop messing around
and put away the smile♪

882
00:43:25,620 --> 00:43:29,520
♪Even mad but don't be forced to smile♪

883
00:43:29,970 --> 00:43:34,330
♪People's characters change♪

884
00:43:34,330 --> 00:43:38,130
♪As time passes and tastes change♪

885
00:43:38,540 --> 00:43:43,000
♪Just laugh without caring for elegance♪

886
00:43:43,000 --> 00:43:46,990
♪Be unique, don't be ordinary♪

887
00:43:46,990 --> 00:43:51,020
♪Let go of lasting memories,
be grateful♪

888
00:43:51,290 --> 00:43:55,620
♪Let go of all struggles
and stubbornness♪

889
00:43:55,620 --> 00:43:59,900
♪Fill the house with freedom. Be free♪

890
00:43:59,900 --> 00:44:03,210
♪Let go of childhood dreams♪

891
00:44:03,210 --> 00:44:06,290
♪And hesitations♪

892
00:44:22,000 --> 00:44:26,390
♪Don't need a broad shoulder
to cry over♪

893
00:44:26,390 --> 00:44:30,120
♪Tears sink into the soil♪

894
00:44:30,490 --> 00:44:34,960
♪Grow into a tree where birds nest♪

895
00:44:34,960 --> 00:44:38,730
♪Passersby, put aside your worries♪

896
